title: Project Zomboid 2.9.9.17 (0012a) *Fixed Torrent*
description:
Cracked and all ready to go.

Project Zomboid one of the latest versions, found on some German website that has since been taken down. http://iload.am/de/thread/106531--MULTI--Project-Zomboid--immer-aktuell-/

Common bug with this version is that the doors to the south and east of your character will not open by mouse click, use the 'e' key standing next to it and it works fine. This version fixed the black screen after loading from the last version uploaded to TPB so this version will fix your save like it did for mine. 

Keep uploading any latest version you guys find if possible and I will do the same.

Also, if they lowered the price to 10 bucks it'd be more reasonable.
